{
  "stem": "13238.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we got terribly scared because now we didn't know what is happening to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Or we are going to be gassed and destroyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Each and every one was shaking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They ask us to undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we walked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember like today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My brother took me around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We'll survive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I didn't believe, because I saw the end of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We still hug each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we went to a very big shower room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What hit me, the shower heads were approximately 6 inches diameter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But normally, a shower head has 2 and 1/2 to 3 inches diameter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we got terribly scared again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they closed the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were standing maybe for 15 minutes, each and every one shaking, didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We're on a brink of death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And finally, water came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because we didn't know what to expect-- or the gas, what they called the Zyklon gas at that time, or the water.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Luckily, the water came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Naturally, everybody was started to jump for joy, because we saw-- we went through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And possible now we have a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "After that was-- I remember like today-- was a very cold and rainy evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They started to drag us around the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had to run, like six in a row, all around the camp, for maybe 2 hours, naked, without any clothing whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We came back again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they gave us-- each and everybody got slacks and a shirt or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they ask us to go to a very big room, where 801 people had to sit and spend the night sitting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But it wasn't space for 801 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we had to spread our legs like eagles.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
